ActPublic Service Rearrangement and Transfer of Duties Act
PrecisOrder (a) transferring the control and supervision of the Population and Public Health Branch from the Department of Health to the PUBLIC HEALTH AGENCY OF CANADA; and (b) directing that the Minister of Health shall preside over it; effective September 24, 2004.
